def generate_key_combinations(T, test_cases):
    results = []
    for t in range(T):
        (A, B) = test_cases[t]
        key_combinations = []
        P = len(str(B))
        index = 1
        for i in range(len(str(A)) - P + 1):
            x = int(str(A)[index:index + P])
            key_combinations.append(x * B)
            index += 1
        results.append(key_combinations)
    return results
